                            >calmo</placeName> cum suis pertinentiis. et <rs key="#Churches"
                            >Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3009">Sancti Andree </orgName>que est in <rs
                            key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Villages/settlements" ref="#places/571"><geogName
                                key="#City_territory" ref="#estates/1913"
                            >suesse</geogName></placeName>. cum omnibus que modo possidet et
                        dominatur et que ei pertinent. et <rs key="#Churches">Ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3008">Sancte
                            Marie</orgName> et <orgName key="#Churches"
