                                ref="#estates/3010">Ceraso</geogName></placeName> quam <rs
                            key="#heirTo">heredes</rs> Ugonis blanci dederunt monasterio et <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortos</rs> et <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >curtisanos</rs> qui sunt prope muros averse. sicut Ugo blancus dedit
